==Starting off==
* '''Father Reen:''' Excuse me, I'm looking for [player name]. I have an urgent job for [him/her].
* {{tselect|Start the Shadow of the Storm quest?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** '''Player:''' That's me!
** '''Father Reen:''' Thank Saradomin I found you!
** {{tcond|If the player still has Silverlight:}}
*** '''Father Reen:''' I believe you still have the magical sword Silverlight?
*** '''Player:''' The sword I used to defeat the demon Delrith? Yes, I still have it.
